acker can send bulk emails to the victim","weakness":{"id":65,"name":"Business Logic Errors"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":1098700,"file_name":"2.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rb4zivay0awzkbl8vkyzzsy6a62j?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%222.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%272.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQ6Q7LE23M%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T083513Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQD89%2F02d1cHdrUV1MbFWOJ5ke6Za7uczudQw2c%2FrnZD0gIhAPVin0%2FV70VgUHMUtzzC%2BODrx7rPLYKCTP3Uhk5Uv8j5KrsFCPD%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQAxoMMDEzNjE5Mjc0ODQ5IgzdJ28GgBZebhpSG%2FsqjwU4KEexjUBaU8MWvfVk0Bjliok%2FpP3sVUEAFGQRQ9Foo6R4d73MTbVLhxn5VOuSh3Y7nMMzIYXfkS5UEgkMybh5ycYWbMnAJwgds9mp0cW6NQ2HAPROCZss8Ra6JAHfxiVkG0C0ushppbcnCBie0oCjUo%2BPj8WrOa8vU7PIuhPLsXH65HJizSDUKTx%2FBZkXshy5bVF%2FYGL%2F0LloAzfiukw3kdrfBc38YrD77PeeQiQak45N%2F7L0SJ0g7szbTcS1lrvdUg%2BgAp9D9GTQo%2FurwDDh1PSji1QDO2pE%2FaqLUATsJgY4hAqfNmccOX1g9S2CqEP9UZJ2XCVVIulPsXVqmsw83zDq7yIkWqgbPfHT4dP1H7lIFKoNOfoXqKMprdA2qOye%2Bi0vBFKdmsYj1e5VM86jcPIcy%2BVTUcoPvF%2BWJyIE1VlNtYt6EAEy34aIC0DA7hQdKy6pXXuT0%2FllXLz5E3o4sz6NI1vDuzwIjQb%2FC7KGQn5mRAhV6%2BnMCqh8t9ZRfl21HDR90xhmaGUFo1o6X1bKCAQ3bNmX047ClTtt4l8SZbJhNIPwZk%2FvJ%2BBlbF%2FBPSRdKlvMbnf%2FVCTscUjwnwJObrdltq8Zu8wlics%2Fx3TBOpvsTdk8tVBhEyxeVSFZZPOI0lTFMvbFx1Lvm2IpOLmCZKPVCO5YqyQ5amngtcSabsjrqeZ80IHFqr4SVui%2FLYRX0cycmbeGt4btr6GqPZnW0EfJI1rBoGKSgB6PSkPMdHfcebTTKbta%2Fqdyqnyub36HeFLJmppvXjZL9J8amNoFQWzTGDNvD4K6yVDyexk%2Bhwdql5%2BVIF7x6RE%2F7ce9kU%2Flkq5kLG40GnvV5jd9baMLzZ9H9nRFevTveKaam2ZCMJXixs8GOrABGaKccx9%2FEEw2eDnQjN%2BhpDXBvyzN99rJaSZgoHWSo3E2a%2F8%2BCC5%2B93yK21%2BeZSK4xcfG1P%2Fr4Rd74EHoVo5so6teFaQ6RYynGsSuqD1nb5pTuzwsMBXZiQvDEJk313SnV0%2FXBoZp9iDgj%2FFdt5Pn0a5